  Cloud infrastructure maintenance schedule must be logged as event 
in this section. The posted event is listed in calender view of both admin and 
users. This options is used to show the current health status of cloud service.

 !adminguide/cloud/11.png!

 h3. ADD/EDIT/DELETE event

            Admin users are able to add event schedule. Login as admin user in 
side menu click Cloud,maintanance then use option add to add schedule maintenance
events.

 !adminguide/cloud/12.png!

 *Add event page contain following elements:*

   Zone: Select zone you want add maintenance
   Cloud Maintenance Date: Date to choose maintenance will perform.
   Desc: Detail about maintenance
  
 To edit and delete events just select the event in calander. The selected event 
have the options of edit and delete.

